00067 typedef struct {                  
00069   int ndim ;                      /* last dimension greater than 1 (1..7) */
00070   int nx,ny,nz , nt,nu,nv,nw ;    /* dimensions of grid array */
00071   int dim[8] ;                    /* dim[0]=ndim, dim[1]=nx, etc. */
00072   int nvox ;                      /* number of voxels = nx*ny*nz*... */
00073   int nbyper ;                    /* bytes per voxel */
00074   int datatype ;                  /* type of data in voxels: DT_* code */
00075 
00076   float dx,dy,dz , dt,du,dv,dw ;  /* grid spacings */
00077   float pixdim[8] ;               /* pixdim[1]=dx, etc. */
00078 
00079   float scl_slope , scl_inter ;   /* scaling parameters */
00080 
00081   float cal_min , cal_max ;       /* calibration parameters */
00082 
00083   int qform_code , sform_code ;   /* codes for (x,y,z) space meaning */
00084 
00085   int freq_dim ,                  /* indexes (1,2,3, or 0) for MRI */
00086       phase_dim , slice_dim ;     /* directions in dim[]/pixdim[]  */
00087 
00088   int slice_code ;                /* code for slice timing pattern */
00089   int slice_start , slice_end ;   /* indexes for start & stop of slices */
00090   float slice_duration ;          /* time between individual slices */
00091 
00092   float quatern_b, quatern_c,     /* quaternion transform parameters   */
00093         quatern_d, qoffset_x,     /* [when writing a dataset,  these ] */
00094         qoffset_y, qoffset_z,     /* [are used for qform, NOT qto_xyz] */
00095         qfac                 ;
00096 
00097   mat44 qto_xyz ;                 /* qform: transform (i,j,k) to (x,y,z) */
00098   mat44 qto_ijk ;                 /* qform: transform (x,y,z) to (i,j,k) */
00099 
00100   mat44 sto_xyz ;                 /* sform: transform (i,j,k) to (x,y,z) */
00101   mat44 sto_ijk ;                 /* sform: transform (x,y,z) to (i,j,k) */
00102 
00103   float toffset ;                 /* time coordinate offset */
00104 
00105   int xyz_units , time_units ;    /* dx,dy,dz & dt units: NIFTI_UNITS_* code */
00106 
00107   int nifti_type ;                /* 0==ANALYZE, 2==NIFTI-1 (2 files),
00108                                                  1==NIFTI-1 (1 file) ,
00109                                                  3==NIFTI-ASCII (1 file) */
00110   int intent_code ;               /* statistic type (or something) */
00111   float intent_p1, intent_p2,     /* intent parameters */
00112         intent_p3 ;
00113   char intent_name[16] ;
00114 
00115   char descrip[80], aux_file[24];
00116 
00117   char *fname ;                   /* header filename (.hdr or .nii) */
00118   char *iname ;                   /* image filename (.img or .nii)  */
00119   int   iname_offset ;            /* offset into iname where data starts */
00120   int   swapsize ;                /* swapping unit in image data (might be 0) */
00121   int   byteorder ;               /* byte order on disk (MSB_ or LSB_FIRST) */
00122   void *data ;                    /* pointer to data: nbyper*nvox bytes */
